Name: libcfile
Version: 20130809
Release: alt2

Summary: Library for cross-platform C file functions
License: LGPLv3+
Group: Development/C

Url: http://code.google.com/p/libcfile/
#Git-Clone: http://code.google.com/p/libcfile
